{
  "stem": "2723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I do recall that, amazingly, either he chose to overlook my skin condition-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I have no explanation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I passed that dreadful muster week after week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we, after the muster, were thrown into the snow for health reasons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember this terror of being thrown into the snow and then coming in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I presume winter was well and truly on the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I was in Auschwitz probably [INAUDIBLE] somewhere-- January or something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] rumor had it that the front was getting close, and they were gradually taking people away, and I was one of the many that were taken away.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a-- after a long, criss-cross train trip through a fair few bombings, we landed in Ravensbruck, which was to be, indeed, a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, we went through the same sort of ordeals of registering and endless, endless standing in one spot and nothing happening.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if somebody collapsed, there was trouble.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we were being taken to work in a quarry in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was daily, every day, in the snow, in the quarry work, which was, I think, the hardest time of all.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no danger to being gassed there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't have crematoria.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the physical work was almost beyond endurance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every day.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- I remember my job was to lift rocks, drag them to a precipice, and roll them down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I can assure you, there was nothing at the bottom of that precipice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was really Sisyphus type of torture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And extremely, extremely damaging to our health.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, we got back every night to the barracks, had some hot food.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
